{"tid":1234520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好緊急﹗處理政府拖延戰略﹗","createTime":"2019-06-17T02:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T10:15:01.000Z","uid":229880,"like":371,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"1cef9a8a38ba43f68a8b38cf1348df1332a0dae8","tid":1234520,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:37:09.000Z","msg":"唔該唔好再互屌﹗<br />\n長長地，但請睇到第3點嘅升級策略﹗<br />\n <br />\n1) 佔定唔佔？<br />\n政府一拖再拖，消耗民意。<br />\n <br />\n今朝令我地出現左夏愨道去留嘅爭議，政府仲要排無gear嘅女警出黎，明顯就係要贏鏡頭同民意。依家電台已經不斷報緊，「警方派出談判專家，但示威者不願離去，沿線一帶封路」等。<br />\n <br />\n我地無本錢互屌，請回想呢個星期點解會有民意。<br />\n <br />\n過去一個星期，衝得到社會認同，係因為9/6晚政府聲明回應及後暴力警犬、11/6學生係地鐵被圍、12/6警犬武力等等。不過，絕大部分市民嘅不滿亦已經係16/6已經發洩左。今朝再衝一定唔會得到佢地支持。<br />\n <br />\n我地呢個星期同政府互有膠著，全因為勇武和理非全部人配合，我地亂陣腳必輸無疑。記住我地每一位都好重要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n今日政府明顯轉陣，要我地輸民意。<br />\n咁我地何不主動撤離，令市民睇見我地訴求唔係無理？更可以俾到前線兄弟休一休息，更利用呢個機會黎再處民意。<br />\n <br />\n2) 對政府回應，大家已經有爭議，點算？<br />\n <br />\n我地呢面要加強文宣，重申「撤回」係最基本的對話起點，及後<br />\n包括平反612、撤消暴動定性、釋放被捕者等等要求。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n3) 政府繼續拖可以點做先？<br />\n <br />\n政府認定已經回應左，等緊民意反彈。<br />\n部分市民可能都覺得回應左，咁當我地贏左呢次。<br />\n點解唔去爭取更多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n見到一眾巴打已經由長輩圖升級去「真建設」，網上聯署等聲明愈黎愈到肉，我就諗點解我地每一次都係見到有問題去防守，唔係去爭取新議題。<br />\n <br />\n記唔記得點解12/6，我地會受到民眾支持，因為我地事前set左deadline。<br />\n政府一直拖，我地就應該將「議題」升級，開更高嘅價，用時限唔俾佢拖﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n雖然愈來愈多人識得登記做選民，但係今次熱情一過，下次選區議員、立法會議員等，再有DQ事件，你肯唔肯定100萬人出黎反？一定唔得，我地呢班人都唔團結。而政府更可以倒轉講，「上次你有100萬人我先撤，今次你地得30萬人？點解要回應&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n <br />\n因此，我地要盡可能係大家仲有熱情時，建立200萬人嘅共同目標，再不斷用呢個數字施壓。<br />\n <br />\n例如︰由200萬人反送中，<br />\n轉去今星期嘅200萬人反明日大嶼、下星期反國歌法等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由於立法會討論有期，對政府就係一個明確嘅時限。<br />\n <br />\n當我地迫到政府回應，佢就要將不利香港人嘅議題「暫一暫緩」先，雖然我地唔係要階段性勝利，但最少咁樣係為香港人爭取最大利益。<br />\n <br />\n點解講講下唔衝？唔係唔衝，而係站出黎係一個低成本而持續嘅方式俾絕大部分香港人參與。記住，香港人今日連罷工都做唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n如果所有呢d議題都同樣地反，立法會長期開唔到會，咁對政府、對大陸黎講，一樣係管治失效。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n結果政府最終都要回應，<br />\n甚至我地可以將議題帶到去普選等。<br />\n <br />\n以上純粹發夢時諗到。<br />\n <br />\n希望大家保持兄弟爬山精神。<br />\n <br />\n見到今朝大家互屌好傷人，我地唔輸得呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97552dc20f08b22ecc98161e75573e60111a6e2","tid":1234520,"uid":229880,"like":120,"dislike":0,"score":120,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:37:53.000Z","msg":"4) 如果同意上述方向，<br />\n<br />\n我地應該係呢幾日即刻做明日大嶼、國歌法嘅文宣<br />\n將呢兩個議題同反送中類比。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有兩至三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油<br />\n<br />\n我地無本錢互屌呀⋯⋯"},{"pid":"2ee714a68da0991aa4f858d497d8f4e390332d75","tid":1234520,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3868991d92a40d5e274b0b60ac6472929a7b3bf7","tid":1234520,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d127dc314e1c080c85e2f99815835b3ae4de54bb","tid":1234520,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:39:32.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25507703851084dff2227e9ea18fe58893f44bbf","tid":1234520,"uid":13754,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:39:39.000Z","msg":"英超踢38場先有冠軍，而我哋只係踢咗幾場互有得失嘅波，未去到4月都未知冠軍花落誰家<br />\n<br />\n如果而家只係因為有失波，有黃牌就覺得失敗<br />\n<br />\n咁你同考第二都會喊嘅林鄭有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家放棄行動一兩次就會有成果嘅期望，預備自己去打持久戰<br />\n<br />\n1. 鍛鍊身體，令自己更強壯，保護自己，保護我哋嘅兄弟姊妹<br />\n2. 學定急救，噚日遊行嘅急救人手真係好唔夠<br />\n3. 去睇敵人對付我哋嘅方法，我哋一齊去諗策略<br />\n<br />\n我哋只要堅持，我哋只會離成功愈嚟愈近，離失敗愈嚟愈遠，唔好忘記曼德拉坐咗咁耐監，佢冇放棄<br />\n<br />\n佢喺監獄日日健身做掌上壓，就係為咗迎接勝利嘅一日"},{"pid":"dc89ace3c7b1d7a7c083c5f3ec5fa6d90e52751f","tid":1234520,"uid":149267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhh"},{"pid":"f4a9f36694457285a3acd7a6e5903a3808ea0ac5","tid":1234520,"uid":251414,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:40:21.000Z","msg":"叫民陣宣布，叫人 撤退"},{"pid":"ade1029d6c34da6b469386da008b4baa7f5ff4fd","tid":1234520,"uid":251414,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4a9f36694457285a3acd7a6e5903a3808ea0ac5","tid":1234520,"uid":251414,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:40:21.000Z","msg":"叫民陣宣布，叫人 撤退"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:40:35.000Z","msg":"唔好畀人屈咗先"},{"pid":"5666e782cc94bc0690c34e0159c346c8d7e8af7f","tid":1234520,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a573e5f428939bacdf3fa32d7e1cb20e5e21c91b","tid":1234520,"uid":167987,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:42:19.000Z","msg":"義士未釋放 條例未撤回 再討論去爭取更多都只係紙上談兵<br />\n坐這山望那山 一事無成"},{"pid":"376080d32664d76ca6d6196914ee110930d2ff90","tid":1234520,"uid":30791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:42:21.000Z","msg":"唔一定要佔 佢拖我地可以策略性撤退 或者開闢其它戰場<br />\n但一定要團結 一定要留住道氣 要維持道德高地<br />\n要堅持到底 不屈不撓 就會有希望"},{"pid":"aa2d739ed61a29fd6eca672bdb0bdce11724eafc","tid":1234520,"uid":2106,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"都話 國歌法 明日大嶼 同反送中唔同，冇咁有爭議性<br />\n<br />\n你唔好當依家有二百萬人，另外兩條都有二百萬人出嚟先得架"},{"pid":"2c53c31263ecf514630e1ec02b889157c4b1cf10","tid":1234520,"uid":15850,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:43:17.000Z","msg":"我建議就係設下死線，要求政府回應。問題要一個一個咁解決"},{"pid":"9c99fc2b0431ea0ecd9055b9d944099aaaa0a7bb","tid":1234520,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"poah"},{"pid":"97fc9fb6f2a527b798eda8a062f3024bbba16487","tid":1234520,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:43:47.000Z","msg":"明日大嶼 同 國歌法 兩個戰場唔係咁易打 要睇下有幾多人反對"},{"pid":"792cf61dcafd29cc23d8a7c0b5f5349bc540e21a","tid":1234520,"uid":53870,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"其實大家日撚日講雨傘<br />\n雨傘都係佔路 最後？<br />\n佔路唔係唯一方法<br />\n仲有好多野可以做架<br />\n一齊行落去啦手足"},{"pid":"a388287d1683ce1e110913e608bbe2a638ba6259","tid":1234520,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e3109efe18db5b6ec0d596889f091c16cef5ee","tid":1234520,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:45:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fd4b57060e839b3c79e3c34650b09603c3fc0cf","tid":1234520,"uid":72344,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:48:10.000Z","msg":"推 手足唔好覺得走左就係輸左 黎緊仲有好多戰場需要你地 一定要用民意令林鄭平反"},{"pid":"a6a7734f087b75455289241c8124ff8deb6e4c89","tid":1234520,"uid":82547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:48:57.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"4afa52c3a4c65